      "role": "user",
      "content": "elevate it to the ceiling? lol that sounds a bit intense. but i can definitely do the ice and rest part. i'm just worried about the walking thing. if i try to walk on it a little bit just to get to the kitchen, is that gonna make it worse or is it fine? i'm just really trying to avoid an expensive trip to the urgent care clinic if i don't have to.",
