      "content": "wait, did you just call me a doctor? i'm not a doctor haha. i'm just an office worker. anyway i'm just really trying to figure out if i should just wait it out. if i do the RICE thing and take some ibuprofen, do you think it's safe to just wait 3 or 4 days before i even think about seeing someone? i'd rather just stay home and rest it if it's just a sprain.",
